  m_Name: R1_2_CollectStrawberry
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  dialogueLines:
  - Now, the tonic itself requires two simple ingredients.
  - First, a strawberry. Sweetness helps stabilize restorative magic.
  - Bring one back when you can.
  - If you need seeds, Hal has of various kinds in his shop.
  - 'We still need a strawberry. '
  - Even simple ingredients can carry strong restorative properties.
  - Perfect.
  - Strawberries help stabilize the tonic's healing properties.
